#   the official gRPC team's pure-JavaScript reference
#   implementation, in continuous active development by Google's
#   gRPC team within the `grpc/grpc-node` monorepo at github.com/
#   grpc/grpc-node.  At 4,500+ ★ on GitHub and 13M+ weekly npm
#   downloads, it is the dominant Node.js gRPC dependency by an
#   order of magnitude — the only mature pure-JavaScript gRPC
#   implementation (the alternatives — the legacy `grpc` package
#   with native C++ bindings, `nice-grpc` which itself depends on
#   @grpc/grpc-js, `@improbable-eng/grpc-web` which is browser-
#   only — either depend on grpc-js under the hood or address
#   different ecosystems).
#
