#       `grpc.credentials.createSsl(rootCertBuffer, privateKey
#       Buffer, certChainBuffer, verifyOptions)` /
#       `grpc.credentials.createFromMetadataGenerator(genFn)` /
#       `grpc.credentials.createFromGoogleCredential(googleCreds)`
#       typed credentials factories
#     • Typed `grpc.Server` with `server.addService(serviceDef,
#       impl)` /  `server.bindAsync(addr, creds, callback)` /
#       `server.tryShutdown(cb)` /  `server.forceShutdown()` typed
#       methods
#     • Typed `grpc.Client` base class with `client.makeUnary
#       Request(...)` /  `client.makeClientStreamRequest(...)` /
#       `client.makeServerStreamRequest(...)` /  `client.make
#       BidiStreamRequest(...)` typed RPC dispatchers
#     • Typed `grpc.loadPackageDefinition(packageDef)` typed
#       package loader that consumes the `@grpc/proto-loader`
#       output and returns typed namespace objects with
#       generated `client` constructors per service
#     • Typed `grpc.Metadata` class with `metadata.set(key,
#       val)` /  `metadata.add(key, val)` /  `metadata.get(key)`
#       /  `metadata.remove(key)` typed methods
#     • Typed `grpc.status.{OK = 0, CANCELLED = 1, UNKNOWN = 2,
#       INVALID_ARGUMENT = 3, DEADLINE_EXCEEDED = 4, NOT_FOUND
#       = 5, ALREADY_EXISTS = 6, PERMISSION_DENIED = 7,
#       RESOURCE_EXHAUSTED = 8, FAILED_PRECONDITION = 9,
