#     • Typed `grpc.ChannelCredentials` /  `grpc.CallCredentials`
#       /  `grpc.MetadataValue` typed primitives
#     • Typed `grpc.connectivityState.{IDLE = 0, CONNECTING = 1,
#       READY = 2, TRANSIENT_FAILURE = 3, SHUTDOWN = 4}` typed
#       connectivity-state enum
#     • Typed `grpc.compressionAlgorithms.{identity = 0,
#       deflate = 1, gzip = 2}` typed compression enum
#     • Typed `grpc.experimental.*` typed experimental
#       extensions (xDS support, advanced load balancers)
#     • Typed `KeepaliveOptions{keepalive_time_ms, keepalive_
#       timeout_ms, keepalive_permit_without_calls}` typed
#       keepalive config
#     • Typed `grpc.makeGenericClientConstructor(methods, name)`
#       typed dynamic client constructor for runtime-known
#       service definitions
#
#   `@grpc/grpc-js` is the gRPC library behind essentially
#   **every Node.js microservice + cloud-native CLI** in
